        public INode createLeafNode(ENodeType typeOfNewNode,
                   java.lang.String dataSetId,
                   com.google.common.collect.Multimap<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object> nominalMeta,
                   com.google.common.collect.Multimap<java.lang.String,java.lang.Double> numericalMeta,
                   IDataset dataset)
        Creates a leaf node of a clustering hierarchy tree with initialized attribute maps.
        Parameters:
        typeOfNewNode - The node type of the new node (User or Content)
        dataSetId - the id of the data set entity that is represented with this cluster tree leaf node.
        nominalMeta - the nominal meta attributes of the data set entity
        numericalMeta - the numerical meta attributes of the data set entity
        dataset - the data set that is processed
        Returns:
        a new INode instance
